# User API Assessment
# 

## Project Setup

#make sure that you install of the independencies to your application
-npm install typescript ts-node express sequelize mysql2 dotenv
-npm install --save-dev @types/node @types/express @types/sequelize eslint prettier eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier

AND for Testing

#make sure you also install all of the indipendencies
-npm install --save-dev jest @types/jest ts-jest



1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/node-typescript-assessment.git
   cd node-typescript-assessment
 
   .env

   DB_HOST=localhost
   DB_USER=root
   DB_PASSWORD=password
   DB_NAME=assessment_db

   npm run dev

   Testing
   npm run test

